ospf
------
conf t
router ospf 3
network 10.0.0.12 0.0.0.3 area 1
network 1.1.1.0 0.0.0.255 area 100
network 1.1.2.0 0.0.0.255 area 100
network 1.1.3.0 0.0.0.255 area 100

virtual link
-------------
conf t
router ospf 3
area 1 virtual-link 10.0.0.13
end
wr

